[action] gets up and clasps hands. … David Bloggs … the one and only … super to see you. Who are you working for? Come and work for me, I'll call you tomorrow. [action] sits down. It's really lovely to have this little chat with you.

00:01:06.000 --> 00:01:12.000
<v Nigel>
Well, I…

