<v Timmy>
I'll get Peter, William, Arthur, Alex, Joan, Ted, Scott, Will, John and Ray to fix it up. It is so nice having this little chat.

00:02:00.000 --> 00:02:08.000
<v Nigel>
Well, actually Timmy, I'm glad to get you on your own…

