00:02:44.000 --> 00:02:48.000
<v Reporter>
Hello.

00:02:48.000 --> 00:03:06.000
<v Timmy>
Peter, this is one of the nicest people in the world, Nigel Watt. [action] Peter scribbles. W-A-double T. That's right, yes.

00:03:06.000 --> 00:03:14.000
<v Nigel>
Well, actually, Timmy, the thing is, it's a bit private.

00:03:14.000 --> 00:03:22.000
[action] A writer comes to the table.

00:03:22.000 --> 00:03:34.000
<v Timmy>
