[action] Timmy smiles and poses. Nigel stops. A photographer hovers.

00:04:38.000 --> 00:05:06.000
<v Timmy>
Do carry on, it's the 'TV Times', only they syndicate these photographs to America. Would you mind if we just er… [action] grabs Nigel by the hand and poses hearty friendship photo. Super, super. One over here, I think, Bob. A little smile, please, smashing, smashing. Feel free, Bob, to circulate, won't you. Do go on, this is most interesting.

00:05:06.000 --> 00:05:14.000
<v Nigel>
Well, the thing is, Timmy, I'm a bit embarrassed.

00:05:14.000 --> 00:05:24.000
[action] Waiter approaches the table.

00:05:24.000 --> 00:05:36.000
<v Waiter (Mario)>
