[action] Director comes in.

00:05:56.000 --> 00:06:10.000
<v Director>
Sorry, sorry, Timmy. Can we just go from where Mario comes in, we're getting bad sound, OK?

00:06:10.000 --> 00:06:22.000
<v Timmy>
